OL,3,CMan charged in connection with
OL,4,Cshooting farmer two years ago in
OL,5,CDerbyshire
OL,7,FA man has been charged with
OL,8,Fmanslaughter more than two years after
OL,9,Fa farmer was shot and killed in
OL,10,FDerbyshire.
OL,12,FThe body of Charles Kinston, who was
OL,13,F23 when he died, was found off
OL,14,FBrizlincote Lane, Bretby, in
OL,15,FDerbyshire on Monday 29 January 2024.
OL,17,FPolice were called just before 6:30pm,
OL,18,Fand Mr Kinston was pronounced dead at
OL,19,Fthe scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
