OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1779909062
OL,3,CMan charged in connection with
OL,4,Cshooting farmer two years ago in
OL,5,CDerbyshire
OL,7,FJoseph Simpkins, 37, of Brizlincote
OL,8,FLane in Bretby, has been charged with
OL,9,Fmanslaughter, possessing ammunition
OL,10,Ffor a firearm without a certificate
OL,11,Fand possessing prohibited ammunition,
OL,12,FDerbyshire police have said.
OL,14,FHe has been released on bail and is
OL,15,Fdue to appear at Southern Derbyshire
OL,16,FMagistrates Court on Monday 15 June.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
