OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1779909062
OL,3,CMan charged in connection with
OL,4,Cshooting farmer two years ago in
OL,5,CDerbyshire
OL,7,FIn a tribute posted on the site
OL,8,FFacebook, Leicestershire and Rutland
OL,9,FYoung Farmers' Club (YFC) described
OL,10,Fhim as a "character" who "devoted his
OL,11,Flove to everyone around him".
OL,13,FIt said: "We are devastated and
OL,14,Fsaddened to announce his life was
OL,15,Ftragically taken away from him (...)
OL,16,Fthe source of laughter for a strong
OL,17,Fclub, Charles prided himself on
OL,18,Fenthusiasm and passion for everything
OL,19,Fhe put his mind to".
